Talk</span><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-accent transition-transform duration-300 translate-y-full group-hover:translate-y-0\"></div></a></div></nav><main><section class=\"relative min-h-screen flex items-center pt-24 pb-12 px-6 md:px-12 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none z-0\" style=\"opacity:1;transform:none\"><div class=\"absolute top-[-20%] right-[-10%] w-[50vw] h-[50vw] bg-accent/10 rounded-full blur-[120px]\"></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-[-10%] left-[-20%] w-[40vw] h-[40vw] bg-[#a920c8]/10 rounded-full blur-[120px]\"></div></div><div class=\"relative z-10 w-full flex flex-col items-center text-center mt-12\" style=\"opacity:0\"><div class=\"mb-8 overflow-hidden inline-block\"><p class=\"text-sm md:text-base tracking-[0.3em] text-foreground/60 uppercase font-semibold\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(100px)\">Creative Digital Studio</p></div><h1 class=\"text-[clamp(2.5rem,5vw,5rem)] leading-[1.1] font-black tracking-tight uppercase font-heading max-w-6xl mx-auto break-words lg:break-normal\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(100px)\">We Create Digital</div><div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-[#b6e949] via-[#fa2472] to-[#7a15df] bg-clip-text text-transparent pb-4\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(100px)\">Experiences That Move.</div></h1><div class=\"mt-10 md:mt-16 flex flex-col items-center gap-8\"><p class=\"max-w-2xl text-lg md:text-xl text-foreground/70 font-medium leading-relaxed\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(100px)\">Clypsea is a creative digital studio blending design, marketing, and technology to build brands that stand out and scale fast.</p><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 mt-4\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(100px)\"><a href=\"#work\" class=\"group flex items-center justify-center gap-4 text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase font-bold bg-foreground text-background px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-accent transition-colors duration-300\">Explore Our Work</a><a href=\"#contact\" class=\"group flex items-center justify-center gap-4 text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase font-bold border border-white/20 px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:border-accent hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-300\">Start a Project</a></div></div></div></section><section id=\"about\" class=\"py-32 px-6 md:px-12 bg-surface\"><div class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"text-[clamp(2rem,4vw,4.5rem)] leading-[1.1] font-black uppercase font-heading mb-16 break-words\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(50px)\">We Don&#x27;t Just Design.<br/><span class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-[#b6e949] via-[#fa2472] to-[#7a15df] bg-clip-text text-transparent pb-2 block\">We Build Momentum.</span></h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 text-lg md:text-xl text-foreground/80 leading-relaxed\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div><p class=\"mb-6\">Clypsea is a multi-service creative agency built for modern brands. We combine strategy, design, and digital marketing to create powerful online experiences.</p><p>We believe creativity should not just look good — it should work. Every project we take is built with purpose, clarity, and measurable growth in mind.</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-col justify-end font-heading font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl text-foreground uppercase tracking-wide gap-4\"><p class=\"border-b border-white/10 pb-4\">We design boldly.</p><p class=\"border-b border-white/10 pb-4\">We build smart.</p><p class=\"text-accent\">We grow brands.</p></div></div></div></section><section id=\"services\" class=\"py-32 px-6 md:px-12 bg-surface\"><div class=\"mb-24 flex flex-col items-start gap-8\"><h2 class=\"text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-black uppercase font-heading\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(50px)\">What <span class=\"text-accent\">We Do</span></h2></div><div class=\"flex flex-col\"><div class=\"group relative grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[60px_1fr_1.5fr_300px] items-start lg:items-center gap-8 py-16 border-t border-white/10 overflow-hidden\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(50px)\"><div class=\"font-heading text-xl text-accent font-bold lg:mt-0\">01</div><div><h3 class=\"text-3xl lg:text-5xl font-black uppercase font-heading group-hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-500\">Creative Design</h3></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-4 text-foreground/80\"><p class=\"text-lg font-medium font-heading\">We design visual identities and digital experiences that leave a lasting impression.</p><ul class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 mt-2\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-foreground/60 group-hover:text-foreground/80 transition-colors\"><span class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent min-w-[6px]\"></span>Branding &amp; Identity</li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-foreground/60 group-hover:text-foreground/80 transition-colors\"><span class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent min-w-[6px]\"></span>Graphic Design</li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-foreground/60 group-hover:text-foreground/80 transition-colors\"><span class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent min-w-[6px]\"></span>UI/UX Design</li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-foreground/60 group-hover:text-foreground/80 transition-colors\"><span class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent min-w-[6px]\"></span>Social Media Design</li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-foreground/60 group-hover:text-foreground/80 transition-colors\"><span class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent min-w-[6px]\"></span>Creative Direction</li></ul></div><div class=\"w-full aspect-video lg:aspect-square lg:h-[220px] rounded-2xl relative overflow-hidden mt-6 lg:mt-0\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center transition-transform duration-700 ease-out group-hover:scale-105\" style=\"background-image:url(https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1561070791-2526d30994b5?q=80&amp;w=2000&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop)\"></div></div></div><div class=\"group relative grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[60px_1fr_1.5fr_300px] items-start lg:items-center gap-8 py-16 border-t border-white/10 overflow-hidden\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(50px)\"><div class=\"font-heading text-xl text-accent font-bold lg:mt-0\">02</div><div><h3 class=\"text-3xl lg:text-5xl font-black uppercase font-heading group-hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-500\">Digital Marketing</h3></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-4 text-foreground/80\"><p class=\"text-lg font-medium font-heading\">We help brands grow, connect, and convert through data-driven marketing strategies.</p><ul class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 mt-2\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-foreground/60 group-hover:text-foreground/80 transition-colors\"><span class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent min-w-[6px]\"></span>Social Media Management</li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-foreground/60 group-hover:text-foreground/80 transition-colors\"><span class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent min-w-[6px]\"></span>Paid Advertising (Meta, Google)</li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-foreground/60 group-hover:text-foreground/80 transition-colors\"><span class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent min-w-[6px]\"></span>SEO Optimization</li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-foreground/60 group-hover:text-foreground/80 transition-colors\"><span class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent min-w-[6px]\"></span>Content Strategy</li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-foreground/60 group-hover:text-foreground/80 transition-colors\"><span class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent min-w-[6px]\"></span>Performance Marketing</li></ul></div><div class=\"w-full aspect-video lg:aspect-square lg:h-[220px] rounded-2xl relative overflow-hidden mt-6 lg:mt-0\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center transition-transform duration-700 ease-out group-hover:scale-105\" style=\"background-image:url(https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551288049-bebda4e38f71?q=80&amp;w=2000&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop)\"></div></div></div><div class=\"group relative grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[60px_1fr_1.5fr_300px] items-start lg:items-center gap-8 py-16 border-t border-white/10 overflow-hidden border-b\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(50px)\"><div class=\"font-heading text-xl text-accent font-bold lg:mt-0\">03</div><div><h3 class=\"text-3xl lg:text-5xl font-black uppercase font-heading group-hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-500\">Web Development</h3></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-4 text-foreground/80\"><p class=\"text-lg font-medium font-heading\">We build modern, fast, and scalable websites that turn visitors into customers.</p><ul class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 mt-2\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-foreground/60 group-hover:text-foreground/80 transition-colors\"><span class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent min-w-[6px]\"></span>Custom Websites</li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-foreground/60 group-hover:text-foreground/80 transition-colors\"><span class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent min-w-[6px]\"></span>E-commerce Stores</li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-foreground/60 group-hover:text-foreground/80 transition-colors\"><span class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent min-w-[6px]\"></span>Landing Pages</li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-foreground/60 group-hover:text-foreground/80 transition-colors\"><span class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent min-w-[6px]\"></span>Web Applications</li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-foreground/60 group-hover:text-foreground/80 transition-colors\"><span class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent min-w-[6px]\"></span>Website Maintenance</li></ul></div><div class=\"w-full aspect-video lg:aspect-square lg:h-[220px] rounded-2xl relative overflow-hidden mt-6 lg:mt-0\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center transition-transform duration-700 ease-out group-hover:scale-105\" style=\"background-image:url(https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1498050108023-c5249f4df085?q=80&amp;w=2000&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop)\"></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"work\" class=\"py-32 px-6 md:px-12\"><div class=\"mb-24\"><h2 class=\"text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-black uppercase font-heading mb-8\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(50px)\">Selected <span class=\"text-accent\">Work</span></h2><div class=\"text-lg md:text-xl text-foreground/70 max-w-2xl font-medium\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><p>Every project is a collaboration.</p><p>Here are some of the brands we’ve helped transform.</p></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-y-16 md:gap-x-8 md:gap-y-32\"><div class=\"group cursor-pointer flex flex-col gap-6 md:col-span-8\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden bg-surface relative rounded-2xl w-full aspect-[4/3] md:aspect-auto md:h-[600px]\"><div class=\"absolute inset-[-15%] w-[130%] h-[130%]\" style=\"transform:translateY(-10%)\"><div class=\"w-full h-full bg-cover bg-center transition-transform duration-700 ease-[cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1)] group-hover:scale-105\" style=\"background-image:url(https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1618005182384-a83a8bd57fbe?w=1200&amp;q=80)\"></div></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-black/20 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 z-10 flex items-center justify-center pointer-events-none\"></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3 group-hover:translate-x-4 transition-transform duration-500\"><h3 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold font-heading\">Aura Branding</h3><p class=\"text-sm tracking-[0.2em] text-accent uppercase font-bold\">Branding | Web Design | Marketing</p><p class=\"text-foreground/70 mt-2\">We crafted a bold visual identity and built a high-performing website designed to convert and scale.</p><div class=\"mt-4 flex items-center gap-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:text-accent transition-colors w-fit pb-1 border-b border-white/20 hover:border-accent\">View Case Study</div></div></div><div class=\"group cursor-pointer flex flex-col gap-6 md:col-span-4 md:col-start-9 md:mt-32\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden bg-surface relative rounded-2xl w-full aspect-[4/3] md:aspect-auto md:h-[600px]\"><div class=\"absolute inset-[-15%] w-[130%] h-[130%]\" style=\"transform:translateY(-10%)\"><div class=\"w-full h-full bg-cover bg-center transition-transform duration-700 ease-[cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1)] group-hover:scale-105\" style=\"background-image:url(https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558655146-d09347e92766?w=1200&amp;q=80)\"></div></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-black/20 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 z-10 flex items-center justify-center pointer-events-none\"></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3 group-hover:translate-x-4 transition-transform duration-500\"><h3 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold font-heading\">Nexus Web</h3><p class=\"text-sm tracking-[0.2em] text-accent uppercase font-bold\">Web Development | SEO</p><p class=\"text-foreground/70 mt-2\">A complete platform overhaul resulting in a 200% increase in user engagement and seamless performance.</p><div class=\"mt-4 flex items-center gap-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:text-accent transition-colors w-fit pb-1 border-b border-white/20 hover:border-accent\">View Case Study</div></div></div><div class=\"group cursor-pointer flex flex-col gap-6 md:col-span-6 md:col-start-2\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden bg-surface relative rounded-2xl w-full aspect-[4/3] md:aspect-auto md:h-[600px]\"><div class=\"absolute inset-[-15%] w-[130%] h-[130%]\" style=\"transform:translateY(-10%)\"><div class=\"w-full h-full bg-cover bg-center transition-transform duration-700 ease-[cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1)] group-hover:scale-105\" style=\"background-image:url(https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1550745165-9bc0b252726f?w=1200&amp;q=80)\"></div></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-black/20 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 z-10 flex items-center justify-center pointer-events-none\"></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3 group-hover:translate-x-4 transition-transform duration-500\"><h3 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold font-heading\">Zephyr Campaign</h3><p class=\"text-sm tracking-[0.2em] text-accent uppercase font-bold\">Digital Marketing | Social</p><p class=\"text-foreground/70 mt-2\">A targeted brand awareness campaign that drove exceptional social reach and customer acquisition.</p><div class=\"mt-4 flex items-center gap-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:text-accent transition-colors w-fit pb-1 border-b border-white/20 hover:border-accent\">View Case Study</div></div></div><div class=\"group cursor-pointer flex flex-col gap-6 md:col-span-8\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden bg-surface relative rounded-2xl w-full aspect-[4/3] md:aspect-auto md:h-[600px]\"><div class=\"absolute inset-[-15%] w-[130%] h-[130%]\" style=\"transform:translateY(-10%)\"><div class=\"w-full h-full bg-cover bg-center transition-transform duration-700 ease-[cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1)] group-hover:scale-105\" style=\"background-image:url(https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1620641788421-7a1c342ea42e?w=1200&amp;q=80)\"></div></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-black/20 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 z-10 flex items-center justify-center pointer-events-none\"></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3 group-hover:translate-x-4 transition-transform duration-500\"><h3 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold font-heading\">Nova UI/UX</h3><p class=\"text-sm tracking-[0.2em] text-accent uppercase font-bold\">App Design | Strategy</p><p class=\"text-foreground/70 mt-2\">Intuitive application design focusing on user retention, frictionless onboarding, and modern aesthetics.</p><div class=\"mt-4 flex items-center gap-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:text-accent transition-colors w-fit pb-1 border-b border-white/20 hover:border-accent\">View Case Study</div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"process\" class=\"py-32 px-6 md:px-12 bg-surface\"><div class=\"flex flex-col xl:flex-row gap-24\"><div class=\"xl:w-1/3\"><h2 class=\"text-[clamp(2.5rem,4vw,4.5rem)] leading-[1.1] font-black uppercase font-heading relative xl:sticky top-32 mb-12 xl:mb-0 break-words\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-50px)\">How We <br/><span class=\"text-accent\">Work</span></h2></div><div class=\"xl:w-2/3 flex flex-col pt-12\"><div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 md:gap-12 pb-16 md:pb-24 border-b border-white/5 last:border-0 last:pb-0 mb-16 md:mb-24 last:mb-0 items-start\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(50px)\"><div class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black font-heading text-accent/50 leading-none select-none w-16 md:w-24 flex-shrink-0 mt-1\">01</div><div class=\"flex-1\"><h3 class=\"text-[clamp(1.5rem,3vw,3rem)] leading-[1.1] font-bold font-heading mb-4 md:mb-6\">Discover</h3><p class=\"text-lg md:text-xl text-foreground/70 max-w-xl leading-relaxed\">We start by understanding your brand, audience, and goals.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 md:gap-12 pb-16 md:pb-24 border-b border-white/5 last:border-0 last:pb-0 mb-16 md:mb-24 last:mb-0 items-start\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(50px)\"><div class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black font-heading text-accent/50 leading-none select-none w-16 md:w-24 flex-shrink-0 mt-1\">02</div><div class=\"flex-1\"><h3 class=\"text-[clamp(1.5rem,3vw,3rem)] leading-[1.1] font-bold font-heading mb-4 md:mb-6\">Design</h3><p class=\"text-lg md:text-xl text-foreground/70 max-w-xl leading-relaxed\">We transform strategy into powerful visuals and digital experiences.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 md:gap-12 pb-16 md:pb-24 border-b border-white/5 last:border-0 last:pb-0 mb-16 md:mb-24 last:mb-0 items-start\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(50px)\"><div class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black font-heading text-accent/50 leading-none select-none w-16 md:w-24 flex-shrink-0 mt-1\">03</div><div class=\"flex-1\"><h3 class=\"text-[clamp(1.5rem,3vw,3rem)] leading-[1.1] font-bold font-heading mb-4 md:mb-6\">Develop</h3><p class=\"text-lg md:text-xl text-foreground/70 max-w-xl leading-relaxed\">We build scalable, high-performance digital products.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 md:gap-12 pb-16 md:pb-24 border-b border-white/5 last:border-0 last:pb-0 mb-16 md:mb-24 last:mb-0 items-start\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(50px)\"><div class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black font-heading text-accent/50 leading-none select-none w-16 md:w-24 flex-shrink-0 mt-1\">04</div><div class=\"flex-1\"><h3 class=\"text-[clamp(1.5rem,3vw,3rem)] leading-[1.1] font-bold font-heading mb-4 md:mb-6\">Grow</h3><p class=\"text-lg md:text-xl text-foreground/70 max-w-xl leading-relaxed\">We launch, optimize, and continuously improve for measurable results.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mt-48 text-center\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.9)\"><h2 class=\"text-[clamp(2rem,4vw,4.5rem)] leading-[1.1] font-black uppercase font-heading tracking-tighter break-words px-4\">We don&#x27;t do <span class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-[#b6e949] via-[#fa2472] to-[#7a15df] bg-clip-text text-transparent\">boring.</span><br/>We build brands<br/>that can&#x27;t be ignored.</h2></div></section><section id=\"why-us\" class=\"py-32 px-6 md:px-12 bg-background border-y border-white/5\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col xl:flex-row gap-24 items-start\"><div class=\"xl:w-1/2 relative xl:sticky top-32 xl:h-fit\"><h2 class=\"text-[clamp(2.5rem,5vw,5rem)] leading-[1.1] font-black uppercase font-heading mb-8 break-words\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(50px)\">Why Choose <br/><span class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-[#b6e949] via-[#fa2472] to-[#7a15df] bg-clip-text text-transparent pb-2 block\">Clypsea?</span></h2><div class=\"text-2xl md:text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-foreground/80 leading-tight pb-8 lg:pb-0\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">We don&#x27;t follow trends.<br/>We create experiences that lead them.</div></div><div class=\"xl:w-1/2 flex flex-col gap-8\"><div class=\"bg-surface p-8 md:p-12 rounded-3xl border border-white/5 hover:border-accent/50 transition-colors group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(50px)\"><h3 class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold font-heading mb-4 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors\">Strategy First</h3><p class=\"text-xl text-foreground/60\">Every creative decision has purpose.</p></div><div class=\"bg-surface p-8 md:p-12 rounded-3xl border border-white/5 hover:border-accent/50 transition-colors group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(50px)\"><h3 class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold font-heading mb-4 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors\">Design With Impact</h3><p class=\"text-xl text-foreground/60\">We create bold, memorable visuals.</p></div><div class=\"bg-surface p-8 md:p-12 rounded-3xl border border-white/5 hover:border-accent/50 transition-colors group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(50px)\"><h3 class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold font-heading mb-4 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors\">Results Focused</h3><p class=\"text-xl text-foreground/60\">Growth and performance matter.</p></div><div class=\"bg-surface p-8 md:p-12 rounded-3xl border border-white/5 hover:border-accent/50 transition-colors group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(50px)\"><h3 class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold font-heading mb-4 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors\">Collaborative Approach</h3><p class=\"text-xl text-foreground/60\">We work with you, not just for you.</p></div></div></div></section><section id=\"testimonials\" class=\"py-32 px-6 md:px-12 bg-surface\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"text-center mb-24\" style=\"op